  abstract={These keynotes discusses the following: Mobile Crowd Sensing and Computing: Challenges and Opportunities; Understanding User Mobility from Large Scale Human Behavioral Data; Assessment of Service Protocol Adaptability in Mediated Service Interactions; VINCE: Exploriting visible light sensing for smartphone-based NFC systems; Personalized Services Based on User Model in Social Networks; Big Data Mining and Computing in a Smart World; A Smart Realtime Video Cloud Platform Using Deep Learning; A Socio-ecological Service Discovery Model in Machine-to-Machine Communication Networks.},
